{"tid":2121674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁卓偉: 第三波疫情的源頭 最有可能是源自多宗輸入個案","createTime":"2020-07-23T12:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T16:17:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f3e7b2370629b4455f583a8029a0a57997c6de73","tid":2121674,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:49:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539488-20200723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539488-20200723.htm&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=180cc79a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539488-20200723.htm&h=c5e311ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539488-20200723.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府專家顧問團成員、港大醫學院院長梁卓偉指出，本港新型肺炎第三波疫情的源頭，並非較早時本地個案群組的殘餘隱型傳播鏈，最有可能是源自多宗輸入個案，相信政府目前的入境檢測措施，已堵塞漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n梁卓偉預計，未來一周的確診數字不會有明顯轉變，要再等多兩星期才回落，要審慎觀望疫情，再決定是否落實更嚴厲的防疫措施。"},{"pid":"75ed0e9d620de47a6d0c6c30e83a637dca6c7784","tid":2121674,"uid":21470,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:51:51.000Z","msg":"係人都知係輸入個案，點會無啦啦爆第三波，係常理<br />\n20.9 萬人次漏洞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec830ac79be2995beee4353f337348e94a5c545","tid":2121674,"uid":359022,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"慶回歸西活動請來大量中國籍婦女歌舞贈慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d65b570698fe058aec90278779241c1fa5b39b2","tid":2121674,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75ed0e9d620de47a6d0c6c30e83a637dca6c7784","tid":2121674,"uid":21470,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:51:51.000Z","msg":"係人都知係輸入個案，點會無啦啦爆第三波，係常理<br />\n20.9 萬人次漏洞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0