20-07-23T12:59:00.000Z","msg":"佢都夠膽講真話？"},{"pid":"6c95069d26f40c6dd7d8f93bd9037a05cd47d568","tid":2121674,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:59:35.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知你老母係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫政府做嘢姐 連尊嚴都冇撚埋<br />\n講嘢講到咁反智<br />\n<br />\n全香港700萬人都知之前就斷尾<br />\n無啦啦周圍同時爆不知明源頭<br />\n唔通有人特登養住啲病毒博中6合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98d3374a7c11f66fff0bcede80270f42fc45e99","tid":2121674,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7G2pPH7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7G2pPH7.png&h=73a0421a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36b8f4bb670cacbc37c57242333386831da2d362","tid":2121674,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過留意<br />\n佢都暗中鳩噏落毒<br />\n幫政府推遲立會選舉做勢<br />\n<br />\n梁卓偉又說，根據早前的研究，若在本地出現爆發期間防疫措施鬆懈，按鬆懈多長時間，需要3至7倍時間才可恢復至原本水平，他估計本港早前鬆懈了大約兩周，料需兩個半月才可恢復至第三波疫情前的水平，即每日新增確診數字維持低水平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200723/s00001/1595496908471/新冠肺炎-梁卓偉研八達通出行數據-病毒即時傳播率料回落至少於1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200723%2Fs00001%2F1595496908471%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%A2%81%E5%8D%93%E5%81%89%E7%A0%94%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A-%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD%E7%8E%87%E6%96%99%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E6%96%BC1&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=5f10dfd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200723%2Fs00001%2F1595496908471%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%A2%81%E5%8D%93%E5%81%89%E7%A0%94%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A-%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD%E7%8E%87%E6%96%99%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E6%96%BC1&h=b9dca626\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200723/s00001/1595496908471/新冠肺炎-梁卓偉研八達通出行數據-病毒即時傳播率料回落至少於1</a>"},{"pid":"154e6b469fb0d83c69d6489084b9d407918681c1","tid":2121674,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46eb700e930d6f90420cc30df6a6fbe915d3c52f","tid":2121674,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:14:01.000Z","msg":"又 spin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91025444ceb8a7b5bedafc8c1aa224c40ebddd99","tid":2121674,"uid":153972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"喺機場亞博館留樣本就堵塞咗漏洞？<br />\n豁免檢疫人士留完樣本唔使等結果就可以走<br />\n等到你有結果，確診病人已同社區有接觸<br />\n<br />\n安排佢哋坐專車，自費住指定過境酒店，餐廳公眾人士唔可以入，先至係有效分隔"},{"pid":"001fb442e2ef8758b9290729f233ee617d17fda0","tid":2121674,"uid":103375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91025444ceb8a7b5bedafc8c1aa224c40ebddd99","tid":2121674,"uid":153972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"喺機場亞博館留樣本就堵塞咗漏洞？<br />\n豁免檢疫人士留完樣本唔使等結果就可以走<br />\n等到你有結果，確診病人已同社區有接觸<br />\n<br />\n安排佢哋坐專車，自費住指定過境酒店，餐廳公眾人士唔可以入，先至係有效分隔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"識咁做就唔係港共啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本連免檢都唔應該有<br />\n仲要船員依啲咁撚高危都免"},{"pid":"a04488e05bc402e060ff4cc7667